item.title: Jennifer Lopez
item.description: Introduction: Jennifer Lopez’s real name is Jennifer Lynn Lopez. Jennifer Lynn Lopez is a famous American actress, singer, dancer, fashion designer, producer, and businesswoman. Jennifer Lopez is one of Hollywood’s driving women who’s likewise manufactured an effective popular and move music profession. Jennifer Lopez is famous for her beauty, her voice, and the amazing style of acting and dance. She is one of the highest-paid American actress and model.
